        "Interest on Capital (max 12%)",
        "Drawing Rights",
        "Admission/Retirement/Death of Partner",
        "Dissolution Procedure",
        "Arbitration Clause",
        "TDS on Partner Payments (NEW: Section 194T from FY 2025-26)"
