        "Sale Consideration",
        "Payment Terms",
        "Title Verification",
        "Encumbrance Certificate",
        "Possession Date",
        "Title Warranty",
        "Indemnification",
        "TDS under Section 194IA",
        "Capital Gains Tax implications"
